That's what I'd do.

124
00:06:26.754 --> 00:06:28.221
-You're not me.
-No.

125
00:06:28.321 --> 00:06:30.357
But then. nobody's you.

126
00:06:30.424 --> 00:06:32.058
Not even you.

127
00:06:33.661 --> 00:06:34.728
By the way.

128
00:06:34.828 --> 00:06:37.297
Samia's alive.

129
00:06:38.499 --> 00:06:40.000
