a clinical nurse as well. ma'am.

156
00:09:00.741 --> 00:09:04.077
Of course. yeah.
Men can be nurses. too.

157
00:09:07.380 --> 00:09:08.515
Okay.

158
00:09:08.582 --> 00:09:10.884
