161
00:09:17.925 --> 00:09:19.827
Yes. ma'am.

162
00:09:21.228 --> 00:09:23.631
Barely the length
of a man's hand.

163
00:09:23.731 --> 00:09:26.166
this nocturnal primate moves...

164
