-For who?

185
00:10:04.972 --> 00:10:06.473
For me. For both of us.

186
00:10:06.573 --> 00:10:08.275
Maybe I could
meet someplace safe.

187
00:10:08.408 --> 00:10:09.943
You could tell me where.

188
00:10:10.043 --> 00:10:12.179
There's this NGO
