190
00:10:13.947 --> 00:10:16.684
They could get me real close
to where you are in Africa.

191
00:10:16.784 --> 00:10:18.952
What's going on?
You been talking to somebody?

192
00:10:19.052 --> 00:10:21.121
Why you want to see me
