193
00:10:21.221 --> 00:10:22.723
I just miss you.

194
00:10:22.823 --> 00:10:25.492
I want to see you.
Check you're okay.

195
00:10:25.625 --> 00:10:29.096
You sound so different.
I'm worried about you.

196
00:10:29.196 --> 00:10:30.698
I miss you. too. sis.

197
00:10:30.798 --> 00:10:32.966
All right. but I need you
