253
00:12:52.873 --> 00:12:55.108
So. he needs a courier.

254
00:12:55.242 --> 00:12:56.409
Here's our play.

255
00:12:56.509 --> 00:12:58.812
Snow White tells Viking
she's desperate.

256
00:12:58.946 --> 00:13:00.347
Flat broke.

257
00:13:00.447 --> 00:13:02.950
